{"tid":1553392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽朝！九月九號 九龍城區 九校要人！","createTime":"2019-09-08T14:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T06:49:04.000Z","uid":23575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"def78a243f490b134b841d1e500b42b4cba30465","tid":1553392,"uid":23575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"希望你地番到屋企見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各校師兄師姐支持下師弟師妹啦！<br />\n聽朝7點見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBCCRGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBCCRGe.jpg&h=a0a58dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/225430_735df04b6f2d15cd5913baa689e6a2ca.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F08%2F225430_735df04b6f2d15cd5913baa689e6a2ca.jpeg&h=6697e5dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oknCRGk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoknCRGk.jpg&h=6297ae54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05b8523d01d19f29393e7d58307edb29c0d8ab26","tid":1553392,"uid":23575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"九月九日九龍城區九校人鏈詳情<br />\n<br />\n日期：二零一九年九月九日<br />\n時間：上午七時正至七時五十分<br />\n<br />\n對象：香港培道中學、民生書院、香港兆基創意書院、喇沙書院、嘉諾撒聖家書院、瑪利諾修院學校(中學部)、東華三院黃笏南中學、賽馬會官立中學、何明華會督銀禧中學校友和在校生<br />\n<br />\n目的：要求政府接受五大訴求及聲援罷課學生<br />\n<br />\nDress code:<br />\n所有參與者:黑口罩、白絲帶<br />\n在校生:校服<br />\n師者: 黑衫黑褲加校章<br />\n<br />\n路線:(如圖2) <br />\n培道主力延文禮士道(經培道門口，不封校門和停車場)和衙前圍道(近九龍仔公園，潮語浸信會對面行人道，不封馬路)<br />\n<br />\n人手分配:<br />\n培道人當日盡量往衙前圍道喇沙方向推進， 每人之間隔兩隻手位👭👫， 在校生盡量企近學校。<br />\n<br />\nRun down:<br />\n7:00-7:15集合(天雨如常，同學切勿進入校門🙅， 入咗去便不能出來)<br />\n7:15開始人鏈👭👭<br />\n7:15-7:50 叫口號+唱歌🎤<br />\n7:50-8:00聯校大合唱🎶🎵<br />\n1do you hear the people sing+試問誰還未發聲<br />\n2無盡<br />\n3願榮光歸香港<br />\n8:00 完結<br />\n<br />\n註:明天人鏈是和平理性的行動，若有藍絲挑釁， 千萬不要被煽動。另外， 請不要封馬路。若封馬路就有可能因作出擾亂秩序的行為， 而構成非法集結。"},{"pid":"71ee228383e83b6b4146aad1ba04fa4b3f7aa809","tid":1553392,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99e90bd1daf2dcee524fa41a227d4646c25146a1","tid":1553392,"uid":176027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7fca4a146db60a215ac396fb0878b99e567ccf5","tid":1553392,"uid":23575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:03:34.000Z","msg":"留意番喇沙仔1拖8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c7d76eeb915f3177af861074adbb12db3bacf4","tid":1553392,"uid":70317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5effa622e1bc6eaeb7fc4c1fd1de5fcc2204e03","tid":1553392,"uid":231345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7d41d2a42583cd83f21502971846b20d62eccc6","tid":1553392,"uid":12523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"咪撚唱無盡屌你老母"},{"pid":"de17f506abc445296c80ccca6fea0f5923672b8d","tid":1553392,"uid":66970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:08:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔唱流行曲，即係無盡"},{"pid":"606389bae5ea1fe4f59f6a5cd07b1d4e69f424e0","tid":1553392,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:10:52.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"39db0079128b842879e50a174fe7095657694aa9","tid":1553392,"uid":104669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"去喇沙門口拖下仔仔隻手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見"},{"pid":"c73945078621643b2da625fe25a7ea0f7600b206","tid":1553392,"uid":20838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit